Name: AuthorizedSourceReference
Description: A reference to the Authorized Source of the value used by this representation. A GeographicLocation may have more than one Authorized Source included in the listing.

Name: GeographicLocationReference
Description: A reference to the GeographicLocation used by this representation.

Name: ExcludedLocationValueReference
Description: A reference to a location value that is excluded, not used by, this representation. May be repeated to exclude multiple location values.
